<p>Logistics cost 14% of GDP india, developed countries = 5-6% of GDP.&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive">GATI SHAKTI</span> = national plan for the development of<strong> multimodal connectivity</strong> to <u><em>economic zones </em></u>and to boost the <strong>last mile</strong> connectivity.</p>
<h3>Reasons&nbsp;</h3>
<p>1. 65% by road&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. multi modal connectivity&nbsp;</p>
<p>3. warehousing etc connectivity , customs,&nbsp;</p>
<p>4. compliance issues&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
